snippet.title: Trench Warfare WW1 - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Trailer for the Trench Warfare WW1, coming February 1 on Google Play and App Store for free. 

Pre-registration available through this link:
https://linktr.ee/simplebitstudios

Or by searching on the store

Music composed by the wonderful Carl Lindegaard.
https://www.carllindegaard.com/
